game.name: Elsa Clothing Store
game.description:
All the princesses have heard the news that new shopping stores have opened up to their nearby places. All except Elsa have already purchased the trendiest clothes and accessories. Now it is the turn of this cute princess. She always wants to visit these stores to keep her up with the latest fashion trends. However, the princess looks uncomfortable while shopping alone. Would you give your precious company to her? Join Elsa Clothing Store and help the princess buy all her needful items!

When you click the play button, you would spot the three stores behind. Choose the store you want to visit and start picking up the items you like in this brand new dressing game for girls! There are plenty of unique designs of top and mini-skirts as well a wide range of elegant gowns to explore in the Clothing Store. In Beauty Salon, you will find out an extensive variety of hairpins, magic sticks, earrings, hats, bags, necklaces and other jewelry times. The Shoe Store will open up various types of designer shoes. 

It will be a great fun to shop with the cute princess in this one of the best girls games. Do your best and keep mixing and matching the items until you spot the most appropriate outfits combined with the fine pair of shoes! Walk to the stores one by one and make sure that the selected items will suit the personality of the cute princess in this html5 dress up game! Good luck to create a combination of fabulous look online, no download required!
